Package com.inchok.aria2

Aria2-A java wrapper of aria2

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DownloadCallback
    The download event listener of Aria2.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Aria2
    The static class which operates the global operations.
    BtMetaInfoData
    The bit torrent meta info data retrieved from ".torrent" file.
    DownloadHandle
    The handle to get the detail information of a specific download.
    ErrorCode
    Error code constants.
    FileData
    The data of files to download.
    Gid
    The unique identifier of each download.
    GlobalStat
    The global statistics of Aria2.
    KeyValues
    The key-value pair list.
    Option
    This is just an empty class, for option names, see Input File of Aria2.
    Session
    The session of Aria2, you need this object through out the download process.
    SessionConfig
    Some additional settings except options.
    UriData
    The uri data get from FileData.getUris().
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BtFileMode
    The mode of bit torrent file mode in BtMetaInfo.
    DownloadEvent
    The type of the download event used in DownloadCallback.onDownloadEvent(Session, DownloadEvent, Gid).
    DownloadStatus
    The status of downloads.
    OffsetMode
    The offset mode used in Session.changePosition(Gid, int, OffsetMode).
    RunMode
    The run mode used in Session.run(RunMode).
    UriStatus
    The uri status used in UriData.
